verbose_text: An example of overlapping mQTL and eQTL signals for RNASET2 (MIM : 612944) on chromosome 6 is presented in XREF_FIG; both RNASET2 expression (SMR p = 6.04 x 10 -8) and DNA methylation at two CpG sites in the first intron of the gene (cg25258033 : SMR p = 2.84 x 10 -10; cg25258033 : SMR p = 2.50 x 10 -10) are associated with Crohn disease (MIM : 266600).
evidence: RNASET2 expression (SMR p = 6.04 x 10 -8 ) and DNA methylation
